name: CLARIDGE Sideboard
description: 4 doors, 2 drawers. Structure, drawer fronts and door frame in solid cherry wood. Top in cherry wood veneer on engineered composite wood, and frame in solid cherry wood. Side panels in cherry wood veneer on engineered composite wood. Back panels in beech veneer on engineered composite wood. 4 shelves in beech veneer on engineered composite wood, and frame in solid beech. Drawer sides and rails in solid oak. Other finishes also available. Manufactured in Europe.
